---
title: One-Pan Greek Spaghetti with Red Pepper Sauce, Feta, Spinach & Fresh Oregano
description: What do you get when you combine bold Greek flavors with spaghetti simplicity? This one-pan wonder! An umami-rich roasted red pepper spread combines with diced tomato and fresh oregano to form a savory sauce, then it’s tossed with al dente spaghetti, baby spinach, and olive oil. The finishing touch? Cheese, of course—because everything’s betta with feta!
